					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Microphone is not in the same set of bits when reading joypad data.  It is in a separate bit of register 4016.  (see <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/Controller_port_registers">http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/Cont ... _registers</a><!-- m --> )<br /><br />The only thing Microphone intersects is the Service button on a VS machine.</div>

					
